The '''Greylands Security Complex''' was a high-security prison on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tentator]]. The facility contained a [[Confiscation Station]], where confiscated vessels were stored after arrests.

The [[Slams]], a gang from [[Mamendin]], managed to escape from the poorly maintained complex, but were recaptured after attempting to break into a [[Commerce Guild/Legends|Commerce Guild]] security vault. The gang's ship, an [[Ubrikkian star yacht]], was held at the Confiscation Station before [[Tyro Caladian]] secured its release, and [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]], and their respective apprentices, [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Ferus Olin]], picked it up.

